network.param.modules.person

Interface IPersonTemplate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBean
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PersonTemplate

    public interface IPersonTemplate
extends IBean
    An interface represents the template information.

    This interface IPersonTemplate will represents template Id, Name, setting the data IPersonTemplate defines below categories of operations:

    • setTemplateID method to set template ID

    • getTemplateID method to get the template ID.

    • setName method to set name.

    • getName method for get the name.

    • setTemplateFields method for set the template fields.

    • getTemplateFields method for set the template fields.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
